OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with showers. The showers,
OL,8,Fespecially across Orkney, becoming
OL,9,Fmore frequent and occasionally heavy
OL,10,Fthrough the early hours. Strengthening
OL,11,Fnortherly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA breezy and rather cold day
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells and showers, most
OL,15,Ffrequent and occasionally heavy across
OL,16,FOrkney in the morning. Strong
OL,17,Fnortherly winds, risk of gales for
OL,18,FShetland later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
