OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Friday, northerly
OL,7,Fwinds easing. Risk of the odd shower
OL,8,FSaturday but mainly dry and bright.
OL,9,FSunday, Orkney rather cloudy with some
OL,10,Frain, Shetland dry and bright.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
